<div class="max-w-xl mx-auto p-4" data-controller="recover">
  <h1 class="text-xl font-semibold mb-2">Recover stuck catches</h1>
  <p class="text-slate-400 text-sm mb-4">
    These are catches saved on this phone that never uploaded. Tap
    <strong>Re-submit</strong> to try again. If a row says
    &ldquo;PHOTO UNREADABLE&rdquo;, tell your organizer &mdash; the image can&rsquo;t
    be recovered from this device.
  </p>
  <p data-recover-target="error" hidden class="text-amber-400 text-sm mb-3"></p>
  <p data-recover-target="empty" hidden class="text-slate-400 text-sm">
    Nothing to recover on this device.
  </p>
  <ul data-recover-target="list" class="text-sm text-slate-200"></ul>
</div>
